text.tspan: This is a game about building your base as big as possible, it's a score attack game.
Live longer to get more points at the end.
Ziggurats gather resources, the one you start with gathers both energy and metals,
unfortunately you can't build any more of those due to patents.
Pylons move resources from one point to another. However they have a little bit of decay
So chaining a lot of them isn't feasible.
However, they *can* shoot the resources over great distances!
(Unfortunately, due too the second law of thermodynamics (everything is awful),
the resources will decay in flight, you won't notice that within 5 tiles travel though)
Resources will only be send to buildings under construction,
or buildings that have less than the sending building has.
Then there are turrets:
These guys help defend you against the enemies that come at night.
They take resources to shoot (blue bar takes energy, grey bar is metal).
